{"tid":1686132,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中年漢倒卧屯門工廈送院不治 現場遺血刀","createTime":"2019-11-01T02:48:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T02:58:24.000Z","uid":222970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0686bc6410a500c6c4e8ee125da4f04b34e43bce","tid":1686132,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:48:29.000Z","msg":"中年漢倒卧屯門工廈送院不治 現場遺血刀<br />\n<br />\n屯門早上發生命案，一名中年男子在建發街開泰工廠大廈內中刀受傷，昏迷送院搶救後不治，警方封鎖大廈調查。<br />\n<br />\n現場為開泰工廠大廈北座2樓保安室對開。事主中刀後昏迷倒地，身上有多處傷痕，身旁有一把染血的刀。現場遺下大片血漬和一件衣服。<br />\n<br />\n保安員於早上6時23分報警求助，救護車將傷者送院搶救，但延至8時30分終告不治。據悉，事主是廠廈其中一名租戶。"},{"pid":"970b17d5fa659a66cc20d907b1321ade9bf23d05","tid":1686132,"uid":53604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:51:23.000Z","msg":"終於都出到明殺"},{"pid":"8c25f032739f463ee8d86570451efd8a809af985","tid":1686132,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:51:43.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721,831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先40%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第二期民調結果POST <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n民調眾籌LINK﹕<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=0d653c62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a>"},{"pid":"1cca3b731e73dc728753c5ea3982cd38eb2c6283","tid":1686132,"uid":301152,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"970b17d5fa659a66cc20d907b1321ade9bf23d05","tid":1686132,"uid":53604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:51:23.000Z","msg":"終於都出到明殺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T03:41:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: violet;\">自插身亡？<br />\n在廁所側的走廊？ <br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rEsbEVe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrEsbEVe.png&h=393ccfac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n較早前：<br />\n屯門建發街發生命案。清晨6時23分，開泰工廠大廈2樓近女廁的走廊，一名中年男子昏迷倒地，身上有傷痕，血流如注，身旁有一把利刀、一件藍色外套及一對黑色鞋，保安員發現連忙報警，由救護車將傷者送院搶救，但告不治。<span style=\"color: orange;\">案件暫列傷人，警方封鎖調查。</span>"},{"pid":"2d773482a737898d6a06fb730517eb2e15099d7a","tid":1686132,"uid":36293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cca3b731e73dc728753c5ea3982cd38eb2c6283","tid":1686132,"uid":301152,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"970b17d5fa659a66cc20d907b1321ade9bf23d05","tid":1686132,"uid":53604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:51:23.000Z","msg":"終於都出到明殺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T03:41:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: violet;\">自插身亡？<br />\n在廁所側的走廊？ <br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rEsbEVe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrEsbEVe.png&h=393ccfac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n較早前：<br />\n屯門建發街發生命案。清晨6時23分，開泰工廠大廈2樓近女廁的走廊，一名中年男子昏迷倒地，身上有傷痕，血流如注，身旁有一把利刀、一件藍色外套及一對黑色鞋，保安員發現連忙報警，由救護車將傷者送院搶救，但告不治。<span style=\"color: orange;\">案件暫列傷人，警方封鎖調查。</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T10:34:44.000Z","msg":"cls, 無可疑"},{"pid":"ce9cc79610a690b943389a58440ef77cde4c43f5","tid":1686132,"uid":95181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:58:24.000Z","msg":"推"}]}